@startuml
state InsertedCard
state WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state MainMenu
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state DispensingCash
state PrintingReceipt
state EjectingCard
state Resetting
state Idle

[*] --> InsertedCard

InsertedCard --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN

ValidatingPIN --> MainMenu : Valid PIN / Display Menu

MainMenu --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Select Withdrawal

ProcessingWithdrawal --> DispensingCash : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash

DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt

PrintingReceipt --> EjectingCard : Receipt Printed / Eject

EjectingCard --> Resetting : Card Ejected

Resetting --> Idle : Reset Complete

Idle --> [*]

Idle : entry / Display Welcome
@enduml
